@Beacon.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

### ──────────────────────────────────────
###  Health Checks
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### Tổng hợp tất cả checks
GET {{Beacon.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json
###

### Liveness — App đang chạy không?
GET {{Beacon.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json
###

### Readiness — DB + MinIO sẵn sàng nhận request không?
GET {{Beacon.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json
###

### Database only
GET {{Beacon.Api_HostAddress}}/health/db
Accept: application/json
###

### MinIO only
GET {{Beacon.Api_HostAddress}}/health/minio
Accept: application/json
###
